data.description: Step into this stunning home, boasting a fluid open floor plan that seamlessly integrates living spaces. The PVC fenced backyard promises privacy and serenity, perfect for family gatherings or quiet evenings. Your fur babies can run free while you enjoy the Florida weather. The heart of this home is its kitchen, a culinary haven featuring luxurious granite countertops and high-quality stainless steel appliances. The large eat-in dinette area adds to the kitchen's functionality and charm. Retreat to the master bedroom, a serene sanctuary offering a spacious walk-in closet. The en-suite bathroom is a haven of relaxation with a separate tub and shower, providing the ultimate comfort. This home is uniquely designed with split jack and jill bedrooms, ensuring privacy and convenience for family and guests alike. The oversized living area is an entertainer's dream, perfect for hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet family nights. Step outside to the covered lanai, an ideal spot for outdoor dining or lounging, overlooking the beautifully landscaped backyard. Located in the desirable Bridgewater community, off of Curley Road, this home is just seconds away from the vibrant lagoon, offering endless recreational activities. Enjoy an easy bike ride to Wesley Chapel High, Wesley Chapel Elementary, and Weightman Middle School, making it an ideal location for families. Experience the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience in this exquisite home, where every detail is crafted for a premium living experience.
